data.description: Welcome to 5300 Morning Sage Way - located in the highly coveted Pacific Highlands Ranch community this stunning Spanish modern home is sure to delight even the most discerning of buyers. This home features a great room that flows organically to the generous outdoor living spaces connected through a wall of disappearing glass and filling the spaces with an abundance of natural light. Enjoy indoor-outdoor living at its finest with a gourmet outdoor kitchen, cozy fireplace and firepit, a lighted water feature making it perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying at any time of day. The interiors are just as stunning with luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, an impressive kitchen with high-end Thermador appliances, an expansive kitchen island and designer light fixtures. The primary bedroom retreat offers a calm and peaceful ambiance with its own living area and a primary bath complete with a spacious shower and soak-in tub, perfect for relaxing and recharging. All of this and so much more in Pacific Highlands Ranch with award winning schools and The Village offering fine and casual dining, speciality grocery stores, boutiques, wellness studios and so much more!Pacific Highlands Ranch is a highly coveted community for good reason due to its amazing location, award-winning schools, numerous parks and recreation areas and The Village is a one-stop destination offering the best fine and casual dining, shopping boutiques, wellness studios and so much more! The Pacific Highlands Ranch community park is the perfect spot to play with five acres of turf field, two dog parks, playground and “discovery play” area, skate plaza, parkour area and bike pump track. There are also baseball fields, a nice area for walking/jogging, fitness stations, picnic areas and basketball courts.
